Title: A New Approach to Superstring Field Theory
Author: Nathan Berkovits (IFT/UNESP, Sao Paulo)
Comments: 9 pages latex, talk given at 32nd Ahrenshoop Symposium
Report-no: IFT-P.034/99
Journal-ref: Fortsch.Phys. 48 (2000) 31-36
\\
  I review the construction of an action for open superstring field theory
which does not suffer from the contact term problems of other approaches. I
also discuss a possible generalization of this action for closed superstring
field theory.
